  lines:
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: ...What does that mean?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\rExactly."
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Is it good? Is it bad? Is it a number? Is it a threat?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Yes.
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I miss when people just said \u201Ccool.\u201D"
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Anyway... why were you in the lake?
